* Atmospheric Model Intercomparison Project (AMIP)
* Atmospheric Radiation Measurement (ARM) (in the US)
* Earth Simulator
* Global Environmental Multiscale Model
* Ice-sheet model
* Intermediate General Circulation Model
* NCAR
* Prognostic variable
* Charney Report

